Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Phase 1 155,000 sq ft of new speculative units from 11,109 sq ft to 31,098 sq ft available Q2, 2020. Jade Business Park is located less than a minute from the A19 immediately south of Murton, County Durham giving excellent access to Tees Valley, Sunderland, Durham and Newcastle upon Tyne with multimodel transport access to the UK and beyond.
